#000000;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><em>d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0&#8221;<\/em><\/span>\u00a0 t\u1ea1i TP.H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\/ TP.HCM v\u00e0 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">&#8220;<em>d\u1ea1y online&#8221;<\/em><\/span>\u00a0 to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Trung:<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">\u00a0 D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m Ti\u1ebfng Trung giao ti\u1ebfp, luy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 <strong>HSK <\/strong>( HSK 1 &#8211; 6 ), luy\u1ec7n thi c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c<\/span><\/li>\n<li><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Trung:<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">\u00a0 D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m Ti\u1ebfng Trung cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, \u00f4n thi chuy\u00ean ng\u1eef, luy\u1ec7n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_GIA_SU_GIOI_CHUYEN_NGOAI_NGU\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>I &#8211; GIA S\u01af GI\u1eceI CHUY\u00caN NGO\u1ea0I NG\u1eee<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh inh<\/strong>\u00a0cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y <strong>CHUY\u00caN ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef TI\u1ebeNG TRUNG: <\/strong>Nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1y <strong>1 K\u00c8M 1 ho\u1eb7c NH\u00d3M cho c\u00f4ng ty, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c <\/strong>t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\/online t\u1eeb L\u1edbp 1 \u0111\u1ebfn L\u1edbp 12, cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i l\u00e0m, c\u00f4ng ty\/ t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Trung<\/strong> <strong>B\u1eaeT BU\u1ed8C <\/strong>\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean\/ c\u1eed nh\u00e2n <strong>GI\u1eceI TOP <\/strong>\u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c khoa ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<strong>\u00a0TI\u1ebeNG TRUNG <\/strong>c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef TOP \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">Gia s\u01b0 <strong>B\u1eaeT BU\u1ed8C<\/strong> ph\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n <strong>GI\u1eceI &#8211; CHUY\u00caN NG\u1eee, <\/strong>ph\u00e1t \u00e2m chu\u1ea9n, ch\u1eafc ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">Gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">T<strong>\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P<\/strong> ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n, gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn <strong>LUY\u1ec6N \u0110\u1ec0<\/strong> b\u1ea5m gi\u1edd theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3858 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU.png 1000w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU-768x461.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gia_su_la_giao_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 110%;\"><strong>?<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean:<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/strong> l\u00e0 c\u00e1c Th\u1ea7y\/ C\u00f4 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p khoa s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m\/ Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Ti\u1ebfng Trung c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef TOP \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i TP.H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">C\u00f3 <\/span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">tr\u00ean 6 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u1edbp d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n thi Ti\u1ebfng Trung,<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">\u00a0<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Cao \u0110\u1eb3ng, \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Trung T\u00e2m d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Gia_su_la_sinh_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><span id=\"%F0%9F%94%B9_Gia_su_la_sinh_vien\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>?\u00a0Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean:<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">&#8211; L\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m Ti\u1ebfng Trung\/ ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Ti\u1ebfng Trung c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef TOP \u0111\u1ea7u: \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef, \u0110H H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0110H S\u01b0 Ph\u1ea1m, \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng&#8230; <\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. \u0110\u00e3 t<\/span><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">r\u1ea3i qua b\u00e0i TEST chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3884 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/GIA-SU-NGOAI-NGU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/GIA-SU-NGOAI-NGU.png 1000w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/GIA-SU-NGOAI-NGU-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/GIA-SU-NGOAI-NGU-768x461.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">? H\u1ecdc 1 k\u00e8m 1 gi\u00fap gia s\u01b0 &amp; h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhau hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_LOI_ICH_HOC_GIA_SU_NGOAI_NGU_1_KEM_1_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>II &#8211; L\u1ee2I \u00cdCH H\u1eccC GIA S\u01af NGO\u1ea0I NG\u1eee 1 K\u00c8M 1 T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian:<\/strong> Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian \u0111i l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: <\/strong>Gi\u00e1o \u00e1n d\u1ea1y <strong>C\u00c1 NH\u00c2N H\u00d3A<\/strong> cho t\u1eebng h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c nhanh h\u01a1n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Linh ho\u1ea1t: <\/strong>B\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cao: <\/strong>Gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft, t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p m\u1ecdi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: <\/strong>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, \u0111\u00fang chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m v\u1eefng, h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 minh b\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p3\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><em>==&gt;&gt; <strong>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u00ed do tr\u00ean, gia s\u01b0 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ed1 1 v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n. <\/strong><\/em><\/span><i><\/i><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_AI_NEN_CHON_HINH_THUC_GIA_SU_NGOAI_NGU_KEM_1_1\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>III &#8211; AI N\u00caN CH\u1eccN H\u00ccNH TH\u1ee8C GIA S\u01af NGO\u1ea0I NG\u1eee K\u00c8M 1:1<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean l\u00e0: Sinh vi\u00ean, h\u1ecdc sinh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i l\u00e0m \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng cao ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean l\u00e0: Sinh vi\u00ean, h\u1ecdc sinh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i l\u00e0m c\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i du h\u1ecdc, xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh cu t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean l\u00e0: C\u00e1c anh, ch\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i l\u00e0m mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n <strong>luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c<\/strong> v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em>N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c anh, ch\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, th\u00ec gia s\u01b0 k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 1:1 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c online 1:1 l\u00e0<strong> l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1.<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em>&gt;&gt; Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi <strong>Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong> ngay h\u00f4m nay theo s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: <strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">096.31.38.511<\/span> <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ho\u1eb7c<\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0862.856.500<\/span><\/span><\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n!<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_NGOAI_NGU_ONLINE_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>IV &#8211; H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af NGO\u1ea0I NG\u1eee ONLINE\/ T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #000000;\"><i style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #555555;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3885 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/Bang-Gia-Tieng-Trung.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/Bang-Gia-Tieng-Trung.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/Bang-Gia-Tieng-Trung-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/Bang-Gia-Tieng-Trung-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><br \/>\n&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i>\u00a0 \u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 <strong><em><span style=\"color: #282828;\">h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed d\u1ea1y online\/ t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/span><\/em><\/strong> tham kh\u1ea3o. H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi chi ti\u1ebft xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 <em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">096.31.38.511<\/span> <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ho\u1eb7c<\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0862.856.500<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/em>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Chinh_sach_hoc_thu\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #33cccc;\"><strong>? Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc th\u1eed:<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><strong>Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong>\u00a0s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u: Trong \u0111\u00f3 gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai bu\u1ed5i, v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc sinh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y, gi\u00e1o \u00e1n, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3812 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-300x201.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-768x515.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"V_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_GIA_SU_TRI_VIET\"><\/span><strong style=\"color: #ff0000;\">V &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH MINH<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">Cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0<strong> MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd &#8211; \u0110\u00daNG &amp; CHU\u1ea8N<\/strong>\u00a0theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 th\u00f4ng tin r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ee9ng minh th\u01b0 &amp; th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">T\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0<strong>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/strong>.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>Gia s\u01b0 <strong>NGHI\u00caM T\u00daC<\/strong> trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>T\u1eadn t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u1ea1y h\u1ebft b\u00e0i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft gi\u1edd.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>D\u1ea1y \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecdc sinh &amp; gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 24\/7 tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><strong>?\u00a0<\/strong>V\u1edbi 12 n\u0103m trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01a1n 15.000+ gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><strong>?\u00a0<\/strong>G\u1ecdi ngay Hotline: <strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">096.31.38.511<\/span> <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ho\u1eb7c<\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <span style=